The paper also mentions the use of citation networks to determine the impact of the paper, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the paper proposes content impact models, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper mentions the use of data-driven models, which could also fall under cs.DL (Deep Learning).
